Subject: [PATCH v4 08/13] platform/x86: oxpec: Add turbo led support to X1
 devices
Date: Tue, 11 Mar 2025 17:54:00 +0100
Message-ID: <20250311165406.331046-9-lkml@antheas.dev>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.48.1
In-Reply-To: <20250311165406.331046-1-lkml@antheas.dev>
References: <20250311165406.331046-1-lkml@antheas.dev>
Precedence: bulk
X-Mailing-List: platform-driver-x86@vger.kernel.org
